[SN]TITLE[SN]
Stormont crisis: "Short window of opportunity

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
The Northern Ireland secretary has said there is now a "short window of opportunity" to resolve the Stormont crisis.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
27 March 2017 Last updated at 17:06 BST
James Brokenshire said there was" no appetite for another election" after the deadline to form a new power-sharing executive passed.
